textBox.richText: Jane opened on Friday...Max and I headed up on Saturday for ATP Devo. They had Gandy and Frenchman open Friday, but looking up those trails today, I can see why they were closed today! They did have the bottoms of Spike and Sterling open...but those were evil. Looks like they’re prepping Cheshire Cat and Sidetrack/Sleeper...hoping that those will open when Gunter is out.
